WEBVTT

01:52.600 --> 01:57.479
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.700 --> 02:01.950
[Episode 21]

02:02.530 --> 02:05.420
[Duanyun Gate]

02:07.180 --> 02:08.180
Your Excellency,

02:08.530 --> 02:11.460
today, before all the officials, we are to

02:11.460 --> 02:13.900
publicly examine the corruption case.

02:14.370 --> 02:16.030
The whistleblower is Fan Yun.

02:16.490 --> 02:17.900
Yet, at this crucial moment,

02:17.900 --> 02:19.360
she's nowhere to be found.

02:19.900 --> 02:20.700
Could it be...

02:21.370 --> 02:23.829
Could it be that she has
a guilty conscience?

02:23.860 --> 02:26.120
Then why hasn't she shown up yet?

02:26.420 --> 02:27.980
Mr. Zheng, calm down.

02:29.930 --> 02:31.090
Let me show you all

02:31.090 --> 02:32.090
something first.

02:32.610 --> 02:33.740
Bring them forward!

02:36.110 --> 02:40.190
-What are these?
-No idea.

02:40.700 --> 02:41.700
Your Excellency,

02:41.980 --> 02:43.180
at Fan Yun's request,

02:43.930 --> 02:45.329
I've brought these four chests

02:45.329 --> 02:47.260
of suspected embezzled treasure.

02:47.530 --> 02:48.490
That's so much.

02:49.090 --> 02:50.050
It really is.

02:50.650 --> 02:52.020
Too much.

02:52.020 --> 02:53.770
Unbelievable.

03:08.000 --> 03:09.000
Mr. Cai.

03:11.210 --> 03:12.810
Come forward and take a look.

03:20.579 --> 03:21.980
What do you think of this?

03:23.460 --> 03:24.460
Your Excellency,

03:24.610 --> 03:27.210
I know nothing about this.

03:27.770 --> 03:29.970
You're the head of the Services Bureau.

03:30.370 --> 03:32.740
Something this serious happened
on your watch,

03:32.740 --> 03:34.520
and yet you're telling me
you knew nothing?

03:34.520 --> 03:36.720
That doesn't quite hold water, does it?

03:36.770 --> 03:37.579
Yes.

03:37.579 --> 03:40.300
Problems did arise within my bureau.

03:40.300 --> 03:41.900
I am willing to accept punishment

03:41.900 --> 03:43.340
for my negligence.

03:43.900 --> 03:45.300
You make it sound so easy.

03:46.180 --> 03:48.420
You'll take responsibility for negligence—

03:48.420 --> 03:49.880
then who, in your opinion,

03:50.370 --> 03:51.329
should answer

03:52.370 --> 03:53.900
for the corruption itself?

03:57.370 --> 03:58.130
Your Excellency,

03:58.130 --> 04:00.840
I truly know nothing about this.

04:03.740 --> 04:05.530
It must have been Lord Lu.

04:06.460 --> 04:07.860
He lined his own pockets!

04:08.770 --> 04:09.860
Lord Cai,

04:09.860 --> 04:10.900
even now,

04:10.900 --> 04:13.230
you're still trying to
pin the blame on me?

04:17.380 --> 04:18.459
Your Excellency,

04:18.459 --> 04:19.529
I'm innocent.

04:23.380 --> 04:24.380
Your Excellency,

04:24.730 --> 04:26.020
may I say something?

04:26.020 --> 04:26.900
Speak.

04:27.940 --> 04:29.200
As far as I know,

04:29.730 --> 04:31.210
the reason Fan Yun was able to uncover

04:31.210 --> 04:33.340
the corruption in the Services Bureau

04:33.460 --> 04:34.850
is precisely

04:34.850 --> 04:38.250
that Lord Lu arranged for her
to audit the accounts overnight

04:39.290 --> 04:41.409
and gave her full access.

04:41.940 --> 04:44.580
If Lord Lu himself
were the one embezzling,

04:45.020 --> 04:48.000
wouldn't he simply be
shooting himself in the foot?

04:48.470 --> 04:50.560
Lord Cai, what do you think?

04:51.140 --> 04:52.140
Your Excellency,

04:52.460 --> 04:53.700
don't listen to Jiang Shu.

04:53.700 --> 04:54.900
He's talking nonsense.

04:54.900 --> 04:57.380
It must be Lord Lu
who broke the law for personal gain.

04:57.380 --> 04:58.260
Your Excellency,

04:58.260 --> 05:00.820
I too was deceived!

05:04.020 --> 05:05.170
Lord Cai,

05:05.370 --> 05:06.890
do you know what this is?

05:07.970 --> 05:09.770
I don't care what it is.

05:09.770 --> 05:13.430
This is a secret medicine I obtained
from the Sacred Rites Bureau,

05:13.700 --> 05:15.530
called the "Truth Pill."

05:15.730 --> 05:17.990
If you have a clear conscience, Lord Cai,

05:18.020 --> 05:19.770
then take this pill

05:19.770 --> 05:22.580
and recount everything
truthfully and in full.

05:23.090 --> 05:24.930
If there's not a single lie,

05:25.330 --> 05:27.210
you can naturally clear your name.

05:27.210 --> 05:29.190
Just because you tell me to take it,
I have to?

05:29.190 --> 05:30.470
Why should I?

05:31.090 --> 05:32.820
But surely you'll listen to me?

05:33.700 --> 05:34.650
I order you

05:35.530 --> 05:36.590
to take the pill now

05:37.170 --> 05:38.630
and prove your innocence.

05:38.770 --> 05:39.770
Your Excellency,

05:39.870 --> 05:41.110
this man Jiang Shu

05:41.210 --> 05:43.850
wears that mask all the time

05:43.850 --> 05:45.940
and never dares to show his true face.

05:45.940 --> 05:48.020
We can't trust his words easily.

05:51.260 --> 05:51.770
Fine.

05:52.580 --> 05:54.650
Since His Excellency asks me to
take the pill, I will.

05:54.650 --> 05:56.460
But if I take the pill today,

05:56.460 --> 05:58.260
do you dare to take off your mask?

05:58.620 --> 06:00.290
If I, Jiang Shu,

06:00.800 --> 06:02.290
remove my mask today,

06:02.620 --> 06:04.220
then you will take the pill?

06:04.770 --> 06:06.060
Fine.

06:06.060 --> 06:07.170
Then I'll show you

06:07.170 --> 06:08.850
my true face beneath the mask.

06:11.110 --> 06:12.960
When does this parade start?

06:12.980 --> 06:14.460
Where is the top-ranked scholar?

06:14.460 --> 06:16.010
It's not time yet.

06:16.580 --> 06:17.980
What about second place?

06:18.500 --> 06:19.460
Second place...

06:19.460 --> 06:20.900
Haven't seen them either.

06:20.900 --> 06:23.820
I heard there's also a female official
among those recommended this time.

06:23.820 --> 06:24.880
A female official?

06:25.530 --> 06:26.850
She's not here either.

06:27.730 --> 06:28.730
Who's there then?

06:30.620 --> 06:32.700
I got here before dawn

06:32.700 --> 06:34.330
just to catch a glimpse of
the top three scholars

06:34.330 --> 06:36.590
and share in their good fortune. Well...

06:36.970 --> 06:38.430
You're far too impatient.

06:40.020 --> 06:42.680
Still, that female official
really isn't here.

06:42.920 --> 06:44.880
I heard the plague
spreading through Yong City

06:44.880 --> 06:46.670
was caused by that very female official.

06:46.670 --> 06:47.900
Every household in Yong City
is in mourning.

06:47.900 --> 06:50.020
They're all waiting to
make her answer for it.

06:50.020 --> 06:51.030
What nonsense!

06:51.210 --> 06:52.409
Why would I lie to you?

07:37.170 --> 07:39.350
You're every bit worthy of
being No. 1 on the Guanyu List.

07:39.350 --> 07:40.880
I have only one word—

07:41.530 --> 07:42.380
impressed!

07:43.500 --> 07:44.580
-Yes, indeed.
-Yeah.

07:44.580 --> 07:45.730
Indeed, he's quite a looker.

07:45.730 --> 07:47.330
I don't deserve such praise.

07:48.380 --> 07:49.190
Lord Cai,

07:50.210 --> 07:52.210
are you feeling a burning sensation

07:52.330 --> 07:53.790
in your stomach right now?

07:54.380 --> 07:55.820
Once this medicine takes effect,

07:55.820 --> 07:57.700
if you don't explain the full story

07:57.700 --> 07:59.460
behind these treasures

07:59.460 --> 08:01.610
within a quarter of an hour,

08:02.730 --> 08:04.940
you will bleed to death
from your seven orifices.

08:04.940 --> 08:06.850
By then, let alone me,

08:07.730 --> 08:09.090
no one can save you.

08:10.090 --> 08:11.770
Think it through yourself.

08:12.460 --> 08:14.020
Listen up, Jiang Shu,

08:14.020 --> 08:15.500
I won't be bluffed.

08:15.940 --> 08:17.410
What evidence do you have

08:17.410 --> 08:19.250
that this treasure

08:19.580 --> 08:21.580
was hidden by me?

08:21.580 --> 08:22.780
Here is the evidence.

08:23.460 --> 08:24.460
Your Excellency,

08:24.460 --> 08:26.330
this pouch contained the congratulatory gold
Tian Xing asked Lord Cai

08:26.330 --> 08:28.410
to send back to his hometown
after passing the selection exam.

08:28.410 --> 08:32.070
It was actually hidden inside
a secret compartment in the coffin.

08:32.900 --> 08:33.809
Lord Cai,

08:34.570 --> 08:35.970
playing all those tricks

08:36.380 --> 08:37.640
to keep everyone away—

08:38.169 --> 08:41.260
you were just afraid
the hiding place would be discovered, huh?

08:41.260 --> 08:42.919
No, Your Excellency, this...

08:43.740 --> 08:44.810
I remember this pouch

08:44.810 --> 08:47.050
was originally in my residence.

08:47.050 --> 08:47.930
It was Lord Lu.

08:47.930 --> 08:49.220
He came to see me once,

08:49.220 --> 08:50.380
and after he left,

08:50.380 --> 08:52.020
the pouch disappeared.

08:52.020 --> 08:53.650
I... I have no idea

08:53.650 --> 08:54.860
how it ended up here.

08:55.220 --> 08:55.770
Your Excellency,

08:55.770 --> 08:57.100
if you don't believe me,

08:57.100 --> 08:58.650
you can send someone to investigate.

08:58.650 --> 09:00.530
That abandoned house and the coffin

09:00.530 --> 09:02.500
are both under Lord Lu's name,

09:02.500 --> 09:03.500
Your Excellency!

09:05.220 --> 09:06.220
Your Excellency,

09:06.730 --> 09:08.410
aside from my own residence,

09:08.740 --> 09:10.070
I own no other property.

09:10.620 --> 09:12.690
I've never heard anyone say
that this treasure

09:12.690 --> 09:14.550
was hidden in an abandoned house.

09:14.570 --> 09:15.650
Lord Cai,

09:15.650 --> 09:18.450
how is it that you remember
that detail so clearly?

09:19.740 --> 09:20.380
I...

09:22.740 --> 09:23.540
Lord Cai,

09:24.140 --> 09:26.220
your time is running out.

09:26.690 --> 09:28.290
You'd better think clearly.

09:31.650 --> 09:32.620
Your Excellency,

09:32.620 --> 09:33.140
I...

09:36.340 --> 09:37.340
Your Excellency,

09:38.570 --> 09:41.260
where power is abused,
injustice is inevitable.

09:41.260 --> 09:43.270
Even if Lord Cai is guilty,

09:43.690 --> 09:46.220
there must be
witnesses and physical evidence.

09:46.220 --> 09:47.510
Now Fan Yun

09:47.740 --> 09:48.760
and Tian Xing

09:49.050 --> 09:51.110
have both disappeared for no reason.

09:51.450 --> 09:52.930
Those so-called receipts

09:52.930 --> 09:54.000
and account books

09:54.620 --> 09:56.150
cannot be verified either.

09:56.740 --> 10:00.090
Doesn't that strike you
as rather suspicious?

10:00.810 --> 10:03.410
The evidence uncovered
by Fan Yun and Tian Xing

10:03.450 --> 10:05.530
naturally needs to be examined
in open questioning.

10:05.530 --> 10:08.100
The auspicious time
for the parade has arrived.

10:08.100 --> 10:09.980
We can't make everyone wait

10:09.980 --> 10:11.580
just because of

10:11.880 --> 10:13.320
those two people.

10:13.340 --> 10:15.220
Yes, yes.

10:18.690 --> 10:21.720
Please order the parade to begin,
Your Excellency.

10:24.170 --> 10:26.370
The auspicious time must not be missed,

10:27.770 --> 10:30.410
but now one of my officials
stands accused of corruption.

10:30.410 --> 10:31.340
The truth

10:32.100 --> 10:33.300
is just as important.

10:33.980 --> 10:37.100
Tian Xing and Fan Yun have arrived!

10:46.530 --> 10:47.740
-Your Excellency.
-Your Excellency.

10:47.740 --> 10:49.000
Please speak, Fan Yun.

10:49.020 --> 10:49.740
Yes.

10:51.410 --> 10:52.410
Your Excellency,

10:52.620 --> 10:53.530
this account book

10:53.530 --> 10:55.390
was sorted out by Tian Xing and me.

10:55.500 --> 10:58.290
Every questionable transaction
has already been marked.

10:58.290 --> 10:59.810
Please review it, Your Excellency.

10:59.810 --> 11:01.020
Lady Fan, please

11:01.020 --> 11:02.380
explain each entry

11:02.380 --> 11:05.020
and answer everyone's questions.

11:06.260 --> 11:07.170
Lord Zheng.

11:27.140 --> 11:29.000
Does anyone else have any doubts?

11:29.530 --> 11:30.530
Your Excellency,

11:31.340 --> 11:33.930
yesterday, Tian Xing and I were taken away
by the Shi family.

11:33.930 --> 11:35.740
They forced Tian Xing to marry

11:36.140 --> 11:38.690
and wanted to kill me
as a sacrifice to the Spirit Immortal.

11:38.690 --> 11:39.770
And all of this

11:39.770 --> 11:41.320
was secretly instigated

11:41.530 --> 11:42.860
by one of the officials.

11:44.860 --> 11:46.770
The Shi family has been brought here.

11:46.770 --> 11:48.700
They can be questioned at any time.

11:50.620 --> 11:51.410
Lord Cai,

11:52.740 --> 11:54.050
confess now,

11:54.740 --> 11:56.470
and I'll count it in your favor.

11:57.570 --> 11:58.450
I...

11:59.570 --> 12:00.580
Just confess.

12:05.530 --> 12:06.440
I confess.

12:07.450 --> 12:08.690
I did

12:09.690 --> 12:11.380
all of this.

12:12.450 --> 12:13.930
All the treasure here

12:14.740 --> 12:16.450
is bribes I've collected

12:17.380 --> 12:20.160
over the years by abusing my position.

12:20.900 --> 12:23.300
And it was also I
who incited the Shi family.

12:23.320 --> 12:24.500
But Your Excellency,

12:24.500 --> 12:25.020
all...

12:26.450 --> 12:28.170
all the treasure is here.

12:28.170 --> 12:30.180
I haven't spent a single coin.

12:30.500 --> 12:31.450
Guards!

12:32.500 --> 12:34.580
Take Mr. Cai away

12:34.980 --> 12:36.340
to await sentencing!

12:36.340 --> 12:37.290
Your Excellency.

12:37.290 --> 12:38.690
Your Excellency, please spare me.

12:38.690 --> 12:40.690
-Your Excellency, please spare me.
-Move!

12:40.690 --> 12:42.930
Your Excellency, could you spare me?

12:42.930 --> 12:44.410
Your Excellency!

12:44.440 --> 12:45.550
Pass my order.

12:46.260 --> 12:48.120
The auspicious time has arrived.

12:48.190 --> 12:49.650
Let the parade begin.

12:50.150 --> 12:55.840
♪ Chase the light,
let our dreams unfold wide ♪

12:55.960 --> 13:00.180
♪ With bold resolve, ignite plain faith ♪

13:00.210 --> 13:02.080
♪ Light them up ♪

13:02.100 --> 13:05.830
♪ Let all wind and frost of days gone by ♪

13:05.970 --> 13:12.040
♪ Turn to countless beams
of light within my eye ♪

13:12.070 --> 13:18.330
♪ Await the sight of you ♪

13:44.190 --> 13:46.900
Still brooding over your father?

13:49.290 --> 13:50.820
Gao Ran told me everything.

13:53.340 --> 13:55.020
His love for you

13:55.570 --> 13:57.180
is actually much deeper

13:57.860 --> 13:59.410
than you realize.

14:02.020 --> 14:04.400
The reason he gave you the surname Yan

14:04.620 --> 14:07.220
was that he hoped you would live

14:07.220 --> 14:08.680
in your own way,

14:08.950 --> 14:10.810
not just as another ordinary Fan.

14:11.100 --> 14:12.790
And this plum tree—he planted it

14:12.790 --> 14:14.590
because you loved eating plums.

14:15.860 --> 14:17.190
Actually, in his heart,

14:18.650 --> 14:20.910
you've long been a part of our Fan family.

14:24.980 --> 14:25.600
Then...

14:26.810 --> 14:28.670
since Father cared for me so much,

14:29.380 --> 14:30.080
why

14:30.410 --> 14:32.290
did he never tell me?

14:33.900 --> 14:35.260
That brother of mine

14:35.740 --> 14:38.490
has never been one to openly express

14:38.650 --> 14:40.500
his likes and dislikes.

14:41.500 --> 14:43.910
Actually, he doesn't like
the family either.

14:43.910 --> 14:45.140
But there are only the two of us brothers

14:45.140 --> 14:46.500
in this generation.

14:46.810 --> 14:48.570
I left the family early on,

14:48.930 --> 14:52.710
so he had no choice but to
carry the family on his shoulders.

14:53.500 --> 14:54.680
The reason

14:54.900 --> 14:56.960
he didn't let you take the surname Fan

14:57.570 --> 14:58.650
was that he feared

14:58.900 --> 15:01.050
you would be entangled

15:01.050 --> 15:03.050
in all the burdens of the Fan family.

15:03.220 --> 15:04.480
Do you understand now?

15:10.810 --> 15:12.740
Thank you for the reminder, Uncle.

15:12.860 --> 15:14.140
I finally

15:14.140 --> 15:16.470
understand Father's deeper intentions.

15:18.140 --> 15:20.450
The academician dinner is about to begin.

15:20.450 --> 15:22.450
Your father is waiting for you there.

15:22.450 --> 15:23.500
You should go.

15:25.560 --> 15:27.020
I'll take my leave, Uncle.

15:46.050 --> 15:48.000
Lord Zhao, a toast to you.

15:48.280 --> 15:50.120
Lord Zheng, a toast to you.

15:50.220 --> 15:50.930
Okay.

15:51.210 --> 15:52.610
Cheers, Lord Li.

15:59.900 --> 16:00.880
Lord Jiang.

16:02.900 --> 16:05.380
I heard that Lord Cai has been

16:05.380 --> 16:09.450
confessing his crimes
one after another in prison.

16:10.650 --> 16:13.110
That Truth Pill of yours
is truly effective.

16:14.980 --> 16:16.170
However,

16:16.170 --> 16:19.450
the Sacred Rites Bureau never
gives its medicine out lightly.

16:19.450 --> 16:21.570
How did you get your hands on it?

16:22.200 --> 16:25.170
How could I possibly obtain medicine
from the Sacred Rites Bureau?

16:25.170 --> 16:26.520
To be honest, Lord Lyu,

16:27.620 --> 16:28.780
that pill of mine

16:29.020 --> 16:32.270
is just herbal dregs
mixed with chili peppers.

16:32.450 --> 16:33.520
Once you take it,

16:33.690 --> 16:35.290
your chest naturally burns.

16:35.450 --> 16:38.290
It's just that Lord Cai
had a guilty conscience,

16:38.620 --> 16:40.260
so he fell for it.

16:43.450 --> 16:45.740
So it was fake?

16:47.260 --> 16:48.020
Not exactly.

16:48.860 --> 16:50.180
It takes

16:50.450 --> 16:52.530
both skill and talent to play the villain.

16:52.530 --> 16:55.220
The more evil deeds you commit,
the heavier the burden on your conscience.

16:55.220 --> 16:56.170
With that weight,

16:56.170 --> 16:58.170
it's not easy to eat or sleep well.

16:59.340 --> 17:01.380
The pill I gave Lord Cai

17:01.900 --> 17:03.810
may well have been the very remedy

17:03.810 --> 17:05.810
that finally eased his conscience.

17:05.900 --> 17:07.369
Jiang Shu, oh, Jiang Shu.

17:07.819 --> 17:11.339
I truly admire you.

17:16.010 --> 17:16.780
Father,

17:17.380 --> 17:18.710
let me offer you a toast.

17:18.730 --> 17:19.380
Alright.

17:26.210 --> 17:28.089
Thank you for raising me, Father.

17:28.620 --> 17:29.650
Do you remember

17:29.650 --> 17:31.510
the day I first came to the family?

17:32.170 --> 17:33.170
Of course.

17:33.690 --> 17:36.250
That day, you ate
three baskets of steamed buns

17:36.250 --> 17:37.780
before you were satisfied.

17:37.900 --> 17:39.340
I only found out later

17:40.010 --> 17:41.740
that I'd eaten your basket too,

17:42.060 --> 17:43.900
leaving you hungry all night.

17:44.620 --> 17:45.450
That was nothing.

17:45.450 --> 17:46.780
I wasn't hungry anyway.

17:47.250 --> 17:48.860
Surnames aren't important.

17:49.970 --> 17:51.140
What matters is

17:52.300 --> 17:53.760
that we are father and son.

17:55.930 --> 17:56.660
Good.

17:57.490 --> 17:58.690
Hearing you say that,

17:58.720 --> 17:59.720
I am

17:59.740 --> 18:01.070
very gratified.

18:07.580 --> 18:08.090
Come on.

18:12.580 --> 18:13.650
Let me tell you,

18:13.820 --> 18:14.820
it's actually good

18:14.820 --> 18:16.750
that you have different surnames.

18:17.170 --> 18:18.270
This way,

18:18.490 --> 18:19.870
you have a chance

18:20.290 --> 18:21.830
to marry Fan Yun.

18:22.540 --> 18:23.060
Marry...

18:23.060 --> 18:24.030
That way,

18:24.490 --> 18:25.320
first,

18:25.340 --> 18:26.980
there's no issue of propriety.

18:26.980 --> 18:27.940
And second,

18:28.820 --> 18:30.990
my adorable niece can marry into

18:31.400 --> 18:32.670
our family.

18:35.850 --> 18:37.160
Listen to Father.

18:37.970 --> 18:38.730
Go on.

18:42.090 --> 18:43.090
Your Excellency,

18:44.210 --> 18:46.070
I can't hold my liquor any longer.

18:48.080 --> 18:49.460
After this full cup,

18:49.910 --> 18:51.510
I'll take my leave.

18:51.820 --> 18:52.710
Alright.

18:52.970 --> 18:54.490
You've worked hard today, Mr. Zheng.

18:54.490 --> 18:55.460
Get some rest.

18:57.540 --> 18:59.140
Thank you, Your Excellency.

19:00.140 --> 19:03.230
Your Excellency,
we'll take our leave as well.

19:03.650 --> 19:04.780
You're all leaving?

19:05.860 --> 19:06.620
Fine then.

19:07.250 --> 19:08.100
Officials,

19:08.100 --> 19:09.210
you should rest early too.

19:09.210 --> 19:10.810
Thank you, Your Excellency.

19:16.030 --> 19:17.960
Why are you all just sitting there?

19:18.380 --> 19:19.580
Let's keep drinking.

19:20.780 --> 19:22.650
I'll go have a couple of drinks
with His Excellency.

19:22.650 --> 19:23.250
Okay.

19:27.930 --> 19:28.610
Cheers!

19:28.900 --> 19:30.320
To Your Excellency.

19:30.780 --> 19:31.900
To you, officials.

19:48.340 --> 19:49.600
Are you looking for me?

20:07.380 --> 20:08.110
You're here.

20:13.750 --> 20:15.670
I... I just got back.

20:15.780 --> 20:16.820
From a blind date?

20:25.080 --> 20:26.480
That's all behind me now.

20:27.170 --> 20:28.060
Yeah.

20:30.490 --> 20:31.190
Gao Ran.

20:33.900 --> 20:35.170
Are you leaving?

20:35.650 --> 20:36.930
I've been sitting for too long,

20:36.930 --> 20:38.460
just getting up to stretch.

20:39.300 --> 20:40.170
That's good.

20:40.580 --> 20:42.640
The banquet is just getting started.

20:45.380 --> 20:47.110
Have a couple of drinks with me.

20:51.530 --> 20:52.500
Welcome back.

21:53.540 --> 21:55.200
Greetings, Your Excellency.

22:04.450 --> 22:05.450
No matter what,

22:06.010 --> 22:07.250
you've finally become

22:07.250 --> 22:08.780
an official of Nine Cities.

22:09.730 --> 22:11.330
Congratulations, Lady Fan.

22:14.340 --> 22:15.940
Thank you, Your Excellency.

22:17.930 --> 22:18.920
Next

22:19.250 --> 22:20.850
is the assignment of duties.

22:21.380 --> 22:22.380
Your Excellency,

22:22.380 --> 22:23.250
I...

22:23.860 --> 22:25.520
have a presumptuous request.

22:28.620 --> 22:29.680
Sit down and speak.

22:35.270 --> 22:36.450
I'd like to take part

22:36.690 --> 22:38.820
in handling the epidemic in Yong City.

22:47.460 --> 22:48.460
You want to go too?

22:50.490 --> 22:51.870
"I want to go too?"

22:52.300 --> 22:53.620
Who else wants to go?

22:55.250 --> 22:56.510
After the parade,

22:57.410 --> 22:59.540
Tian Xing requested permission to go.

23:03.210 --> 23:04.130
No wonder

23:04.820 --> 23:06.380
I didn't see him just now.

23:07.280 --> 23:09.190
So he's planning to go

23:09.710 --> 23:10.960
all by himself?

23:16.780 --> 23:19.180
It's dangerous ahead. How could I possibly

23:19.820 --> 23:21.490
let you go by yourself?

23:22.690 --> 23:25.060
In controlling an epidemic,
two things matter most:

23:25.060 --> 23:26.440
speed and stability.

23:26.890 --> 23:27.630
Speed

23:28.060 --> 23:30.340
means we must quickly
cut off the source of infection

23:30.340 --> 23:31.580
and stop the spread.

23:31.970 --> 23:32.900
I know medicine.

23:33.300 --> 23:35.160
If I go, I can tend to the sick first

23:35.380 --> 23:36.860
and reassure the local people.

23:36.860 --> 23:37.970
Then what about stability?

23:37.970 --> 23:38.820
Stability means

23:38.820 --> 23:40.050
every treatment

23:40.210 --> 23:42.410
must be based on solid evidence
after careful verification.

23:42.410 --> 23:44.740
We can't prescribe medicine recklessly.

23:47.820 --> 23:49.300
What do you need me to do?

23:50.060 --> 23:51.540
The conditions in Yong City are too harsh

23:51.540 --> 23:53.070
for developing medicines.

23:53.340 --> 23:55.730
I can't take
all of Lord Jiang's books there,

23:55.730 --> 23:57.330
nor can I carry all the herbs.

23:57.690 --> 23:59.210
For those already infected,

23:59.210 --> 24:02.340
we still have to rely on
Your Excellency and Lady Fan Yun.

24:02.860 --> 24:04.760
If we don't have sufficient confidence

24:04.760 --> 24:06.290
in handling this epidemic,

24:06.380 --> 24:07.860
sending a large force there

24:07.860 --> 24:09.460
will only make things worse.

24:09.650 --> 24:11.300
I agreed to let Tian Xing go first

24:11.300 --> 24:13.010
because it's his hometown.

24:13.380 --> 24:14.910
He's more familiar with it.

24:15.450 --> 24:16.820
I also need someone to take the lead

24:16.820 --> 24:18.280
and open up the situation.

24:21.180 --> 24:21.970
Yes.

24:23.340 --> 24:24.400
From this point on,

24:24.650 --> 24:27.140
even if there's only
a one-in-a-million chance,

24:27.140 --> 24:28.740
we can't afford to ignore it,

24:28.900 --> 24:29.830
nor can we delay.

24:31.340 --> 24:32.140
That's right.

24:34.930 --> 24:35.490
But...

24:37.010 --> 24:38.870
you must have heard those rumors.

24:40.540 --> 24:41.740
If I put you in charge,

24:42.650 --> 24:44.380
I'm worried there could be danger—

24:44.380 --> 24:45.710
even a risk to your life.

24:52.650 --> 24:53.850
But Your Excellency,

24:54.150 --> 24:55.410
the people of Yong City

24:55.780 --> 24:57.240
are also in mortal danger.

24:57.650 --> 24:59.710
It is exactly because of those rumors

25:00.010 --> 25:01.290
that I must go there.

25:02.860 --> 25:04.320
I'll go solve the problem.

25:04.820 --> 25:05.610
This way,

25:05.930 --> 25:07.860
not only can I
save the people of Yong City,

25:07.860 --> 25:09.720
but I can also dispel those rumors

25:10.460 --> 25:13.390
and become a role model
for future female officials.

25:15.060 --> 25:16.520
It will also show everyone

25:16.690 --> 25:18.420
that Your Excellency's policy

25:18.450 --> 25:20.010
of opening
the civil service examinations to all

25:20.010 --> 25:20.760
is right.

25:22.550 --> 25:24.350
You really want to go that badly?

25:38.930 --> 25:40.730
Actually, I guessed it long ago.

25:42.210 --> 25:43.940
Whatever Fan Yun decides to do,

25:44.260 --> 25:45.520
she'll see it through.

25:49.400 --> 25:52.530
She never considers
how worried everyone else might be.

25:54.490 --> 25:55.340
Well...

25:56.170 --> 25:57.140
Your Excellency,

25:57.140 --> 25:58.550
aren't you the same?

25:58.930 --> 25:59.900
You're right.

26:00.380 --> 26:01.290
That's why I say

26:01.620 --> 26:02.550
that's one thing

26:02.690 --> 26:04.750
we have in common as husband and wife.

26:05.170 --> 26:05.860
Hus...

26:06.610 --> 26:08.400
W-What husband and wife?

26:09.010 --> 26:11.460
Just now, you addressed me as Lady Fan.

26:11.690 --> 26:14.100
I'm your subject now.

26:16.620 --> 26:17.240
Yeah.

26:18.690 --> 26:20.420
Whatever our relationship is,

26:20.860 --> 26:22.320
as long as it involves you,

26:22.730 --> 26:24.190
it means something to me.

26:33.250 --> 26:33.970
Alright.

26:35.060 --> 26:37.120
Tomorrow, before all the officials,

26:37.490 --> 26:39.490
I'll announce that you and Tian Xing

26:39.490 --> 26:41.420
will jointly handle the epidemic.

26:43.580 --> 26:44.830
Great.

26:45.490 --> 26:47.090
Thank you, Your Excellency.

26:50.140 --> 26:53.000
Whether women
can truly become capable officials,

26:53.620 --> 26:54.970
we shall see

26:55.730 --> 26:57.100
starting tomorrow.

27:06.300 --> 27:07.150
Does...

27:07.490 --> 27:08.490
it still hurt?

27:10.860 --> 27:12.250
You mean here?

27:12.900 --> 27:13.760
Or here?

27:16.470 --> 27:19.870
Just a few days apart,
and you've already learned to tease me.

27:21.100 --> 27:22.780
This wound healed a long time ago.

27:22.780 --> 27:23.730
But this one

27:24.340 --> 27:25.550
still hurts a bit.

27:28.730 --> 27:29.560
Sorry.

27:30.250 --> 27:31.750
Actually, last time,

27:32.050 --> 27:33.910
I didn't know if I could come back.

27:33.970 --> 27:35.860
I thought, what if I couldn't come back?

27:35.860 --> 27:37.760
I should at least leave you something

27:37.760 --> 27:39.160
so you would remember me.

27:41.100 --> 27:43.500
Miss Wei, actually, every time you appear,

27:44.060 --> 27:45.920
you leave a deep impression on me.

27:46.010 --> 27:46.850
Then tell me,

27:46.890 --> 27:48.180
do you remember

27:48.200 --> 27:50.000
what I said to you here last time?

27:50.100 --> 27:51.550
I knew you wouldn't.

27:51.860 --> 27:52.490
Last time,

27:52.490 --> 27:54.820
I told you my name is Wei Ying,

27:54.820 --> 27:56.280
and "Ying" means firefly.

27:56.690 --> 27:57.650
It was just like now—you sitting there,

27:57.650 --> 27:58.780
and me sitting here.

27:58.980 --> 27:59.980
Oh,

28:00.360 --> 28:01.250
and also

28:01.270 --> 28:03.450
that time I brought you
the sour plum drink.

28:03.450 --> 28:06.040
I just wanted to add some
extra nutritious ingredients for you.

28:06.040 --> 28:07.200
Who knew

28:07.410 --> 28:09.070
your soldiers would end up...

28:10.650 --> 28:11.490
You know what,

28:11.820 --> 28:13.820
I might actually
have some medical talent after all.

28:13.820 --> 28:14.450
Look,

28:14.450 --> 28:16.100
all those strong,
sturdy soldiers of yours—

28:16.100 --> 28:17.470
one bowl, and down they all went.

28:17.470 --> 28:18.340
Oh, right.

28:18.360 --> 28:19.580
Do you still remember

28:19.880 --> 28:22.330
the first time we met?

28:39.900 --> 28:42.600
♪ Wind sheds rain like tears ♪

28:42.620 --> 28:43.840
♪ Over the whole town ♪

28:43.860 --> 28:46.360
♪ At the second our gazes meet ♪

28:46.510 --> 28:50.080
♪ Past memories roar one louder beat ♪

28:47.730 --> 28:48.540
You see,

28:49.340 --> 28:50.860
you don't remember either.

28:50.860 --> 28:53.210
So how could I not bite you?

28:52.820 --> 28:55.300
♪ Perhaps hearts long to seek ♪

28:53.210 --> 28:54.730
I figured

28:54.730 --> 28:56.100
even after the wound healed,

28:55.320 --> 28:56.680
♪ Etch within our fingertips ♪

28:56.100 --> 28:57.210
the scar would remain.

28:56.710 --> 28:59.600
♪ Hear crisp footsteps echo clear ♪

28:57.210 --> 28:58.300
And if it doesn't,

28:58.300 --> 28:59.820
I'll just bite you again.

28:59.620 --> 29:03.100
♪ Strike out
on a fearless dream's frontier ♪

29:04.510 --> 29:07.850
♪ Though fleeting years rush
without delay ♪

29:06.490 --> 29:07.580
See? See?

29:07.910 --> 29:10.930
♪ A wisp of softness
tints your brow each day ♪

29:08.300 --> 29:09.140
You've got

29:09.140 --> 29:10.970
such an adorable dimple,

29:10.960 --> 29:12.960
♪ Walk side by side with moon and sun ♪

29:10.970 --> 29:12.430
yet you never smile for me.

29:12.980 --> 29:16.100
♪ When all is said and all is done ♪

29:13.140 --> 29:14.820
I

29:14.820 --> 29:16.170
remember everything about you.

29:16.120 --> 29:18.120
♪ We'll ride upstream and downs ♪

29:16.820 --> 29:18.300
But you?

29:18.150 --> 29:20.580
♪ When deep love dwells within our eyes ♪

29:20.620 --> 29:22.650
You don't remember anything at all.

29:20.820 --> 29:23.840
♪ Our burning longing never dies ♪

29:23.970 --> 29:28.770
♪ Wander together through wind and frost ♪

29:28.790 --> 29:30.950
♪ Don't let the sun down ♪

29:36.380 --> 29:37.100
Wei Ying.

29:39.290 --> 29:40.090
Wei Ying?

29:41.930 --> 29:42.550
Wei Ying?

29:42.960 --> 29:45.190
♪ Perhaps hearts long to seek ♪

29:45.410 --> 29:47.210
You look so handsome when you smile.

29:45.460 --> 29:46.810
♪ Etch within our fingertips ♪

29:46.840 --> 29:49.730
♪ Hear crisp footsteps echo clear ♪

29:47.780 --> 29:48.780
You must

29:49.690 --> 29:50.620
remember me.

29:49.760 --> 29:53.230
♪ Strike out
on a fearless dream's frontier ♪

29:54.640 --> 29:57.980
♪ Though fleeting years rush
without delay ♪

29:58.040 --> 30:01.060
♪ A wisp of softness
tints your brow each day ♪

30:00.210 --> 30:01.250
It's hard...

30:01.090 --> 30:03.090
♪ Walk side by side with moon and sun ♪

30:03.110 --> 30:06.230
♪ When all is said and all is done ♪

30:03.860 --> 30:05.170
to forget.

30:06.260 --> 30:08.260
♪ We'll ride upstream and downs ♪

30:08.280 --> 30:10.710
♪ When deep love dwells within our eyes ♪

30:10.950 --> 30:13.970
♪ Our burning longing never dies ♪

30:15.820 --> 30:16.540
The new academicians

30:16.540 --> 30:19.140
have completed
their internship within the residence.

30:19.140 --> 30:20.070
Starting today,

30:20.380 --> 30:22.540
they will be assigned to various bureaus
for further training.

30:22.540 --> 30:23.180
Fan Yun!

30:28.690 --> 30:29.510
I order you,

30:29.820 --> 30:31.220
together with Tian Xing,

30:31.410 --> 30:33.870
to jointly handle
the epidemic in Yong City.

30:36.380 --> 30:37.640
Yes, Your Excellency.

30:38.010 --> 30:39.010
Your Excellency,

30:39.010 --> 30:40.580
I have an objection.

30:41.180 --> 30:43.100
The epidemic in Yong City
is spreading rapidly,

30:43.100 --> 30:44.060
and the situation remains unclear.

30:44.060 --> 30:47.140
How can these two newcomers
shoulder such an important task?

30:47.140 --> 30:47.900
I believe

30:47.900 --> 30:49.580
such a critical matter as epidemic control

30:49.580 --> 30:51.510
should be entrusted to Lord Jiang.

30:51.540 --> 30:53.100
That would be the more prudent choice.

30:53.100 --> 30:55.490
Mr. Jiang now heads the Services Bureau,

30:56.060 --> 30:57.450
with heavy official duties

30:57.450 --> 30:59.150
and multiple responsibilities.

30:59.150 --> 31:00.530
So he only needs to
assist with this matter

31:00.530 --> 31:01.930
and provide support.

31:02.650 --> 31:03.920
As for Tian Xing,

31:04.140 --> 31:04.940
though young,

31:05.410 --> 31:07.270
he has a solid medical background

31:07.380 --> 31:08.920
and is also from Yong City.

31:09.910 --> 31:11.700
He has already gone ahead of everyone else

31:11.700 --> 31:13.570
to assess the situation there.

31:14.140 --> 31:16.070
With him in charge of the epidemic,

31:16.250 --> 31:19.210
we can be confident
everything will proceed smoothly.

31:19.210 --> 31:20.380
Your Excellency,

31:20.780 --> 31:22.180
I second that objection.

31:22.450 --> 31:23.690
May I ask, Your Excellency,

31:23.690 --> 31:24.730
what is the use

31:24.730 --> 31:26.730
of sending

31:26.730 --> 31:27.930
Fan Yun there?

31:29.450 --> 31:31.650
Your Excellency, esteemed officials,

31:32.210 --> 31:33.820
rumors have been spreading

31:34.900 --> 31:37.540
that this epidemic
was caused by a woman holding office.

31:37.540 --> 31:38.560
I believe

31:39.060 --> 31:40.210
controlling the epidemic

31:40.210 --> 31:41.450
is not only about treating the disease

31:41.450 --> 31:43.310
but also about treating the mind.

31:43.340 --> 31:45.140
That is why I wish to
go to Yong City myself

31:45.140 --> 31:46.450
to dispel those rumors,

31:46.450 --> 31:47.450
so that all under heaven

31:47.450 --> 31:48.340
will no longer have objections

31:48.340 --> 31:49.600
to commoners and women

31:49.970 --> 31:51.210
holding official positions.

31:51.210 --> 31:52.270
Well said.

31:53.250 --> 31:55.650
Whoever started the trouble should end it.

31:55.780 --> 31:58.580
Lady Fan, your courage and determination

31:58.580 --> 31:59.920
have earned my respect.

32:00.450 --> 32:02.800
I shall watch with great anticipation.

32:10.490 --> 32:11.380
Zheng,

32:11.380 --> 32:12.380
are you alright?

32:12.380 --> 32:15.310
Done being at odds
with the Fan family's little girl?

32:15.820 --> 32:17.820
Since the boat has already set sail,

32:18.060 --> 32:20.210
rather than trying to stop it,

32:20.210 --> 32:21.070
we might as well

32:21.210 --> 32:23.010
let it ride the wind.

32:23.640 --> 32:25.530
Only I wonder—is your wind

32:25.550 --> 32:27.620
blowing east or west?

32:27.690 --> 32:30.690
Whichever way it blows,
as long as it's strong enough,

32:31.170 --> 32:32.330
it will

32:32.360 --> 32:34.570
carry the boat ashore one day.

32:36.080 --> 32:36.900
Lyu,

32:37.210 --> 32:39.730
what's Zheng

32:39.730 --> 32:41.060
being so cryptic about?

32:41.930 --> 32:43.380
Explain it to me.

32:46.210 --> 32:47.900
He means that

32:48.820 --> 32:51.540
since Fan Yun's becoming an official
is a done deal,

32:51.540 --> 32:53.740
just let her go and make a mess of things.

32:54.060 --> 32:56.860
Epidemics have always been
difficult to contain.

32:57.620 --> 32:59.820
If she makes even the slightest mistake,

32:59.820 --> 33:01.300
he will impeach her.

33:02.380 --> 33:03.780
And he will use that to prove

33:03.780 --> 33:05.910
that women cannot serve as officials,

33:06.730 --> 33:08.770
nor can commoners.

33:11.690 --> 33:12.380
Please.

33:16.430 --> 33:19.530
[Yong City]

34:23.300 --> 34:25.260
The Spirit Immortal comes forth.

34:25.260 --> 34:27.260
The people are saved from disaster.

34:27.260 --> 34:29.219
The holy sect descends.

34:29.219 --> 34:31.699
The sun and moon shine again!

34:29.360 --> 34:30.969
[Chunxiu, Yong City Resident]

34:32.179 --> 34:34.050
The Spirit Immortal comes forth.

34:34.050 --> 34:36.050
The people are saved from disaster.

34:36.050 --> 34:37.900
The holy sect descends.

34:37.900 --> 34:39.929
The sun and moon shine again!

35:01.530 --> 35:03.860
Thank you. Thank you.

35:45.910 --> 35:47.700
[Zhu Luan, Yong City Resident]

35:56.410 --> 35:57.900
I heard the Shi family nobles

35:57.900 --> 36:00.320
left for Ling'an a few days ago.

36:00.490 --> 36:03.150
Someone should be coming
to save us soon, right?

36:04.090 --> 36:05.490
Let's hope so.

36:05.490 --> 36:06.120
Zhu Luan!

36:06.700 --> 36:07.480
I'm back!

36:11.780 --> 36:13.090
Brother!

36:13.090 --> 36:13.800
Zhu Luan!

36:15.410 --> 36:16.570
You're back.

36:18.200 --> 36:19.300
Have you been missing me?

36:19.300 --> 36:19.740
Yes.

36:19.740 --> 36:20.930
Have you been listening to your mother?

36:20.930 --> 36:21.530
Yes.

36:21.530 --> 36:22.130
I have.

36:22.130 --> 36:22.820
Good girl.

37:08.110 --> 37:10.010
These are all the records
we've gathered so far

37:10.010 --> 37:11.810
about the epidemic in Yong City.

37:12.010 --> 37:13.270
They detail

37:13.660 --> 37:15.990
the onset time of patients in each county,

37:16.000 --> 37:17.340
the number of cases,

37:18.010 --> 37:19.610
and their basic conditions.

37:19.680 --> 37:20.390
Great.

37:20.930 --> 37:21.930
These are

37:21.930 --> 37:23.330
all essential right now.

37:26.740 --> 37:28.740
Don't you have anything to say to me?

37:29.080 --> 37:29.950
Tell...

37:30.050 --> 37:30.970
tell you what?

37:34.490 --> 37:36.780
Your Excellency truly plans ahead

37:36.780 --> 37:37.740
with remarkable foresight,

37:37.740 --> 37:38.930
embodies the virtues of a wise ruler,

37:38.930 --> 37:40.450
and lays the foundation
for a flourishing age.

37:40.450 --> 37:42.380
Your Excellency is truly amazing.

37:42.570 --> 37:43.770
I'm not that amazing.

37:43.980 --> 37:44.990
I merely...

37:53.410 --> 37:55.070
Greetings, Your Excellency.

37:55.380 --> 37:56.410
You're here.

37:56.410 --> 37:57.070
Lord Jiang.

37:57.860 --> 37:58.790
Perfect timing.

37:58.900 --> 38:01.300
Fan Yun and I are just
studying the epidemic in Yong City.

38:01.300 --> 38:02.530
This record here

38:02.530 --> 38:04.090
documents the very first case—

38:04.090 --> 38:06.750
it seems to have been
at the beginning of summer.

38:06.780 --> 38:08.180
The symptoms include...

38:09.490 --> 38:10.900
unbearable fever,

38:10.900 --> 38:12.220
continuous groaning,

38:12.220 --> 38:15.080
along with severe headaches and vomiting.

38:15.340 --> 38:16.490
That sounds like

38:16.490 --> 38:18.570
it was caused by some kind of poison.

38:20.700 --> 38:21.860
But this record

38:21.860 --> 38:23.010
shows nothing

38:23.010 --> 38:24.990
unusual in his food.

38:25.410 --> 38:26.220
However, soon after,

38:26.220 --> 38:27.150
his whole family

38:27.380 --> 38:28.860
came down with the same illness.

38:28.860 --> 38:30.010
Not just one family.

38:30.820 --> 38:32.850
It seems the entire village got sick.

38:32.850 --> 38:33.530
Look here.

38:37.700 --> 38:40.740
The spread went from isolated cases
to entire communities.

38:40.740 --> 38:41.820
Could this disease

38:42.570 --> 38:44.260
be contagious?

38:45.090 --> 38:47.010
If it were spread through
person-to-person contact,

38:47.010 --> 38:49.090
the outbreak pattern
should radiate outward.

38:49.090 --> 38:50.860
But the later cases were

38:51.010 --> 38:53.340
in villages even hundreds of miles apart.

38:53.700 --> 38:55.700
It's almost as if the source of infection

38:55.700 --> 38:57.300
can shift places at will.

38:58.490 --> 38:59.270
Lord Jiang,

38:59.380 --> 39:00.700
has Yong City ever experienced

39:00.700 --> 39:02.360
an epidemic like this before?

39:02.620 --> 39:04.350
Yong City lies in a hot climate,

39:04.410 --> 39:05.900
with complex summer weather

39:05.900 --> 39:07.660
and many kinds of snakes,
rodents, and insects.

39:07.660 --> 39:09.900
Various illnesses break out
from time to time.

39:09.900 --> 39:11.630
But I've never heard of one

39:12.130 --> 39:13.530
this contagious before.

39:16.320 --> 39:18.450
At the very least, we've now confirmed

39:18.610 --> 39:20.820
this disease doesn't spread
from person to person.

39:20.820 --> 39:23.280
That's a real blessing
amid the misfortune.

39:28.950 --> 39:30.110
Didn't Lady Fan Yun

39:30.410 --> 39:31.900
declare so boldly

39:31.900 --> 39:33.560
that she'd face the challenge head-on

39:33.560 --> 39:34.820
and dispel the rumors?

39:35.340 --> 39:37.570
Why is she still in Ling'an?

39:38.860 --> 39:40.260
Is she afraid?

39:42.050 --> 39:44.650
See? Being an official
isn't so easy after all.

39:44.700 --> 39:46.930
Commoners becoming officials
is already absurd enough—

39:46.930 --> 39:49.060
what can a woman do as an official?

39:50.010 --> 39:52.220
When it's time to face danger,

39:52.220 --> 39:55.020
isn't it always we men
who stand on the front lines?

40:07.450 --> 40:08.260
Blood!

40:08.260 --> 40:09.260
You're bleeding!

40:10.180 --> 40:11.050
Blood...

40:13.740 --> 40:15.490
Lord Xu? Lord Xu?

40:16.040 --> 40:17.390
Wake up, Lord Xu!

40:18.180 --> 40:18.820
Lord Xu!

40:19.490 --> 40:20.700
Help!

40:21.200 --> 40:22.240
Stop laughing!

40:22.260 --> 40:24.010
What is wrong with you guys?

40:24.150 --> 40:26.010
Can't you see Lord Xu has fainted?

40:26.300 --> 40:28.630
This is the Spirit Immortal Sacred Water.

40:46.410 --> 40:47.770
The Governor's wife...

40:48.660 --> 40:49.900
How has Lady Fan Yun

40:49.900 --> 40:50.850
been?

40:51.050 --> 40:53.780
Has anyone been
making things difficult for her?

40:53.900 --> 40:55.930
Someone is maliciously slandering her,

40:55.930 --> 40:57.660
saying the plague here
is divine punishment

40:57.660 --> 40:59.190
for a woman holding office.

40:59.220 --> 41:00.860
But trouble of that sort

41:00.860 --> 41:02.970
is nothing she can't handle.

41:06.900 --> 41:07.750
True.

41:07.930 --> 41:09.860
Nothing can defeat Lady Fan Yun.

41:10.220 --> 41:12.380
Lady Fan Yun is the strongest

41:12.380 --> 41:14.840
and most optimistic person
I've ever known.

41:15.300 --> 41:16.490
And now,

41:16.490 --> 41:17.600
there is one more.

41:19.260 --> 41:20.090
You.

41:20.970 --> 41:23.380
How could I possibly be
compared to Lady Fan Yun?

41:23.380 --> 41:24.970
Zhu Luan told me everything.

41:24.970 --> 41:25.860
If you hadn't

41:25.860 --> 41:27.380
held things together all this time,

41:27.380 --> 41:29.930
this pharmacy would've become
a house full of the living dead.

41:29.930 --> 41:31.660
You've done an incredible job.

41:37.780 --> 41:38.490
You don't know

41:38.490 --> 41:40.050
what I've done in the past.

41:42.050 --> 41:43.710
No matter what you did before,

41:44.090 --> 41:45.260
here in Yong City,

41:45.260 --> 41:47.790
you're already someone
everyone looks up to.

41:56.660 --> 41:57.860
The water's boiling.

42:02.610 --> 42:03.780
What's this?

42:04.130 --> 42:05.030
Miss Suyin,

42:06.300 --> 42:07.160
do we have wine?

42:07.530 --> 42:08.110
Yes.

42:28.260 --> 42:29.670
Alum?
